FBIS4-40858 "drsov119_r_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-119 Daily Report 18 Jun 1994 Azerbaijan Paper Says Kusarskiy Rayon Lezgins Slain by Azeris Paper Says Kusarskiy Rayon Lezgins Slain by Azeris PM2006130994 Moscow NOVAYA YEZHEDNEVNAYA GAZETA in Russian 18 Jun 94 p 1 PM2006130994 Moscow NOVAYA YEZHEDNEVNAYA GAZETA Russian BFN [Report by Eldar Zeynalov under the "Azerbaijani News" rubric: "Interethnic Tension in Kusarskiy Rayon"] [Text] There has been a sharp increase in nationalistic propaganda in Kusarskiy rayon, which has a concentrated population of Lezgins, following the 15 June killing of four Lezgin policemen by Azeris. The body of one of them was set up in the central square of Kusary, the rayon center, causing local Lezgins to gather.
